title: Fullmetal Alchemist 2 - Brotherhood - 01(H264) 480p
description:
This is In Japanese with English Subtitles.

"Fullmetal Alchemist - Brotherhood" is a new animated series based on the manga of the same title. It is the second adaptation(The original series being the first) , aiming to follow the original manga's storyline more closely, as opposed to the original series which had a differencing  storyline from the manga. However there will be some similarities between the two series.
